      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "and thrust me through. His armour-bearer would not",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". He refused the request or bidding of Saul, no doubt mainly in respect of the fact that Saul was still \"the anointed.\" We have a full description of both the loose arms and of the armour of the body in the case of the Philistine Goliath (",
